~~~

### With User Extension

The page:

~~~ .yaml
---
title: Page Title
author: @ta-tau-taufik
...

Page content.
~~~

The user file as `lot\user\ta-tau-taufik.page`:

~~~ .yaml
---
link: http://example.com
author: Taufik Nurrohman
...

Page content.
~~~

The property call:

~~~ .html
<a href="<?php echo $page->author->link; ?>" id="<?php echo $page->author->key; ?>">
  <?php echo $page->author; ?>
</a>
~~~

or:

~~~ .php
<?php echo $page->author; ?>
~~~